   ```c
   int main() {
      const char* folderPath = "C:/Path/To/Your/Folder";
      deleteFiles(folderPath);
      printf("All files deleted successfully.\n");
      return 0;
   }
   ```
   Make sure to update the `folderPath` variable with the actual path of the folder you want to delete files from.
7. Save and compile the C code using an appropriate compiler.
